{
  "text": "AAVs. There have been controversies in the efficiency of AAVmediated transfection of human HSCs. It has been reported that AAV2-mediated transgene expression in CD34 1 cells is transient, presumably because of inefficient integration. [CITATION_1] Several groups have shown successful transduction of human CD34",
